name: s30 240z G-Nose canvas print
description:
Yet another illustration of one of the car's I'm kind of partial towards. Printed on high quality canvas and pre-stretched. Print measures 11.5"x24".

limited to 20 pieces.

International shipping available as well, please email for a quote.

Please be patient when ordering canvas prints, since each one is made per-order, a process that could take up to 3 weeks including shipping.

name: 4" Under Construction sticker - white or clear background
description:
Wear it loud! For all of us who are in the midst of building our dream rides, here's a sticker representing that labor of love. 

Vibrant red graphic on a white or clear background. 4" diameter vinyl circle sticker.

set of 3.

name: Datsun 240z - small canvas print
description:
This is a smaller version of the large canvas print of the Datsun 240z. This print measures 7.5" tall by 23" wide.

Like the rest of my work on canvas, this print is limited to 20 pieces.

"SAMPLE" watermark text does not appear on the actual paper print.

for international shipping, please inquire via email @ dsalni.drawn@gmail.com

name: 240z Print on canvas ver 2.0
description:
Due to multiple inquiries and requests, here's version 2.0 of the large canvas print of the Datsun 240Z.

Just like the original, the new print measures 15.5"x48". Canvas pre-stretched over a frame. This particular print in the above size is limited to 10 pieces.. 

signed and numbered.

name: 240ZG large print on canvas
description:
Here's the latest addition to the canvas print line-up. It's an S30 G-Nose Fairlady.

The canvas measures a huge 48"x19" and comes stretched over a frame. 

Please enquire about international shipping costs. Loose (off the frame ) versions are available for $20 less.

The print is limited to 10 copies.

*watermark "dsalnidrawn.com" does not appear on actual print!*
